Author: cobwebs4brains
Text: Someone at my work asked me what my diet plan is, because I’ve lost a lot of weight.. instead of saying “low carb” or “counting calories” or “keto” or literally anything... I was like “yeah I don’t really eat. I don’t really have any healthy dieting advice..” and she just stared at me like a deer in headlights.. wtf is wrong with me

Author: Yoni1660
Text: I’ve done this before. Pretty easy to play off as a joke but still terrifying
